twoSetSkill.name: Dynamite 2 Pieces
twoSetSkill.description: When Charged ATKs hit the enemy, generate an explosion centered on host that deals 180.0% of Physical DMG to nearby enemies. CD: 1s.

threeSetSkill.name: Igniter 3 Pieces
threeSetSkill.description: After each entry, the first 2 hits taken by the host will suffer 40.0% Total DMG Reduction and not interrupt her. Crit DMG of Charges ATKs increases by 30.0%. Explosion DMG of Dynamite increases to 200.0% ATK of Physical DMG.
